{"tid":1628150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中文系學生冒死進言，和暴大獅子兄，勿裝修書店。","createTime":"2019-10-06T00:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:50:07.000Z","uid":143284,"like":63,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"7ba3261d44686965bfcf15cd7e6a15bdcea9aaf2","tid":1628150,"uid":143284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T00:57:13.000Z","msg":"預左比大家屌五毛都要講，書籍係文化既象徵，唔止中文系學生，好多和理非同埋老一輩都唔會中意呢個舉動，其實大家如果想支持港資書店，點解唔做好文宣黎宣傳港資/抵制三中呢?而家唔係你燒完佢地就會收皮，三中背後係國家，錢多到你燒都唔會燒得曬，而家仲要同時有國際戰線打緊，係咪要海外華人同埋美國都覺得我地係新紅衛兵，肆意破壞文化象徵先滿意?之前立法會無人破壞圖書館都係一樣道理，點解而家咁多五毛吹風爆呢樣個樣?再思考下solomon佢地琴日講乜野？政府呢幾日既異常行動？<br />\n<br />\n最後，大家想下，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燒書焚書既人係邊個？秦始皇、項羽！望各位慎之戒之，我地係正義之師，勿墮圈套</span></span>"},{"pid":"e0c55e7b06b34d982ef32d2c4c28864c7782b4f5","tid":1628150,"uid":143284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T00:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請各位保持理智"},{"pid":"5c282b6e06b2d854fa0d1b7f7fbf1c0f49d2d932","tid":1628150,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:01:26.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"44402b96f31db5df0090ab1f7eb9382828372da3","tid":1628150,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:01:36.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"66ef441b01f4b4cf94e58de65981268c9998fc5f","tid":1628150,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:01:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0f3c9bab14ee01ec14a0c15ff6c3f35f5529405","tid":1628150,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3a6987773e83842278cc680bfaf83a5980d31c","tid":1628150,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:02:05.000Z","msg":"裝修咪武宣囉<br />\n裝修完再Justify咪得"},{"pid":"e3b3df83885f78af75888fd1be06ce46363408b9","tid":1628150,"u